precis:
Variation of Orders No. R-38000 and No. R-39638 of the National
Transportation Agency, authorizing VIA RAIL CANADA INC. to discontinue
operating its service between Montréal and Halifax via Saint John
(the "Atlantic") effective December 17, 1994, which will terminate all
rail passenger service between St-Hyacinthe, Quebec and Moncton,
New Brunswick via Sherbrooke, Quebec and Saint John, New Brunswick.
